cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it introduces a novel framework for generative models based on Restricted Kernel Machines. It also proposes a novel training procedure to update the parameters of the network. 

It is also likely to belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the framework incorporates multi-view generation and can incorporate Convolutional based models. 

Additionally, it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a new approach to generative modeling. 

It may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it can incorporate (deep) neural network models. 

Finally, it could belong to cs.SD (Sound) as the framework can be applied to generate audio samples.
